headline: CarMax Announces Third Quarter Conference Call
summary: RICHMOND, Va., November 26, 2024--CarMax, Inc. (NYSE:KMX) will report its financial results for the third quarter ended November 30, 2024 before the market opens on December 19, 2024, and it will host a conference call with investors at 9:00 a.m. ET to discuss these results.
